      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.0yJjfyvWg5pDLcVR]{Conditions}</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You move at half speed, you can&rsquo;t run or charge, and you take a &ndash;3 penalty to your Armor Class, attack rolls, melee damage rolls, thrown weapon damage rolls that add Strength to damage, Reflex saving throws, initiative checks, and Strength- and Dexterity-based skill and ability checks.</p>\n<p>The amount of bulk you can carry without becoming @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.OwZA6flUQPH0jPA0]{Encumbered} is reduced by 3.</p>\n<p>After 1 hour of complete rest, you instead become @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.JGFn4MrDZ6X5vrzU]{Fatigued}.</p>"
